---
title: Caribbean-Style Prawns & Veggie Rice Bowl  with Charred Corn Salsa & Aioli
description: The rice is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh prawns in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk
seasoning and roast veggies with a zap of corn salsa and aioli drizzled over at the end.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with brown rice due
to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663c67a892f430b61ffd6507-f1488d6c.jpeg
